description: Assigns attributes (key and value pairs) to the findings that are specified by the ARNs of the findings.

parameters.name: findingArns
parameters.description: The ARNs that specify the findings that you want to assign attributes to. (string) ---

parameters.name: attributes
parameters.description: The array of attributes that you want to assign to specified findings. (dict) --- This data type is used as a request parameter in the  AddAttributesToFindings and  CreateAssessmentTemplate actions. The attribute key. value (string) --- The value assigned to the attribute key.

nested_params.name: value
nested_params.description: The value assigned to the attribute key.

nested_items.name: failedItems
nested_items.description: Attribute details that cannot be described. An error code is provided for each failed item.

nested_items.name: failureCode
nested_items.description: The status code of a failed item.

nested_items.name: retryable
nested_items.description: Indicates whether you can immediately retry a request for this item for a specified resource.
